    <item>
      <title>विद्याप्रशंसा</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/kAvyam/laxyam/champUH/nItiH/hitopadeshaH/sarva-prastutiH/upadeshAH/vidyAprashamsA/vidyA/</link>
